    "visualHierarchy": "Visual hierarchy is achieved by utilizing consistent spacing, clear labels, and grouping settings logically. The app bar provides clear indication of screen context. The text styles (Body/Medium for labels, Caption/Small for supporting text) aid in creating clear visual distinctions and reducing visual noise."
